ucares, o almidón y azucares por el procedimiento de doble fermentación, alcohólica y acética. El vinagre contiene una cantidad especifica de ácido acético."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xDef_7981dd46","http://art.uniroma2.it/ontologies/vocbench#hasSource":"PROPOSED DRAFT REVISED REGIONAL STANDARD FOR VINEGAR. CODEX STAN 162-1987 (revoked)","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2026-01-12T13:22:30"},"dct:modified":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2026-01-12T13:24:20"},"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#value":{"lang":"en","value":"Vinegar is a liquid, fit for human consumption, produced exclusively from suitable products containing starch and/or sugars by the process of double fermentation, first alcoholic and then acetous. Vinegar contains acetic acid."}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_ar_1299513103663","type":"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#Label","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2002-12-12T00:00:00Z"},"http://rdfs.org/ns/void#inDataset":{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/void.ttl#Agrovoc"},"skos:notation":{"type":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/AgrovocCode","value":"8253"},"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#literalForm":{"lang":"ar","value":"خل"}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_be_517e0c73","type":"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#Label","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2025-08-26T12:05:49"},"http://rdfs.org/ns/void#inDataset":{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/void.ttl#Agrovoc"},"skos:notation":{"type":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/AgrovocCode","value":"8253"},"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#literalForm":{"lang":"be","value":"воцат"}},{"uri":"http://aims.fao.org/aos/agrovoc/xl_cs_1299513103681","type":"http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#Label","dct:created":{"type":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime","value":"2003-03-27T00:00:00Z"},"http://rdf